Romney Backs Permanent Changes Over Temporary Payroll Tax Cuts

-- B y   B o b   D r u m m o n d
-- 
2011-10-12T01:50:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/romney-backs-permanent-changes-over-temporary-payroll-tax-cuts.html
Former Massachusetts Governor Mitt
Romney said he favors “permanent changes to the  tax code ” over
President  Barack Obama ’s proposal for temporary reductions in
the  payroll tax .  “I don’t like temporary little Band-Aids,” Romney said.  Romney spoke at a debate among Republican presidential
candidates sponsored by Bloomberg LP and The Washington Post in
Hanover,  New Hampshire .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bob Drummond in Washington at 
 bdrummond@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jim Rubin at 
 jimrubin@bloomberg.net  